OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FA rare glimpse of a young puffin
OL,7,Femerging from its nest has given
OL,8,Fconservationists fresh hope for the
OL,9,Ffuture of Dorset's dwindling puffin
OL,10,Fpopulation.
OL,12,FFor the first time in 30 years,
OL,13,Fvolunteers monitoring the puffin
OL,14,Fcolony in Purbeck have a confirmed
OL,15,Fsighting of a puffin fledgling ` known
OL,16,Fas a puffling ` on the cliffs near the
OL,17,FNational Trust's Dancing Ledge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
