PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784728097
OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FThe puffling was peeping out from a
OL,7,Fdeep crevice on the sheer cliff, where
OL,8,Fthe last breeding colony of puffins on
OL,9,Fmainland England's south coast is
OL,10,Fclinging to survival.
OL,12,FThe sighting followed more than 15
OL,13,Fweeks of monitoring by the volunteers
OL,14,Fas they watched the adult puffins
OL,15,Fcourting, mating, carrying nesting
OL,16,Fmaterial and, since late May,
OL,17,Frepeatedly delivering fish to the
OL,18,Fnests hidden deep within the crevice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
