PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784728097
OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FIf it survives, it may return to
OL,7,FPurbeck from around two years of age,
OL,8,Falthough puffins do not usually breed
OL,9,Funtil they are around four years old.
OL,11,FIn April, six adult puffins were
OL,12,Frecorded at the colony.
OL,14,FBy early June, volunteers had observed
OL,15,Fpuffins carrying fish into at least
OL,16,Ftwo separate nesting locations on the
OL,17,Fcliff, indicating that more than one
OL,18,Fpair may have been attempting to raise
OL,19,Fchicks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784728097
OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FHowever, only one pair was regularly
OL,7,Fdelivering fish to a nest site visible
OL,8,Ffrom the monitoring point ` the
OL,9,Flocation where the puffling was later
OL,10,Fseen.
OL,12,FWhile other puffins were also observed
OL,13,Fcarrying fish to different parts of
OL,14,Fthe ledge, these deliveries ceased
OL,15,Fafter June 12, suggesting that any
OL,16,Fchicks in those nests did not survive
OL,17,Fto fledging.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
