PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784728097
OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FDr Caldow said: "Seeing the puffling
OL,7,Fwas a great thrill, the first puffling
OL,8,Fthat's been recorded in Purbeck for a
OL,9,Flong time.
OL,11,F"It tells us that Purbeck puffins can
OL,12,Fstill lay fertile eggs, hatch them
OL,13,Fand, at least in some years, find
OL,14,Fenough food to rear a chick and escape
OL,15,Fthe attention of predators."
OL,17,FThe 13 volunteers took turns to
OL,18,Fobserve the nesting ledge,
OL,19,Fcontributing around 150 hours of their
OL,20,Ftime.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
