PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784728097
OL,3,CRare puffling sighting offers hope for
OL,4,CDorset's dwindling puffin colony
OL,6,FAdditional puffin sightings were
OL,7,Fprovided by commercial boats run by
OL,8,FDurlston Country Park, Birds of Poole
OL,9,FHarbour and Pierhead Watersports.
OL,11,FIn March 2026, the National Trust
OL,12,Frenewed its efforts to understand why
OL,13,Fthe puffin colony has been failing to
OL,14,Fproduce chicks.
OL,16,FMotion-sensor cameras, powered by
OL,17,Fsolar panels, were installed by high
OL,18,Fropes experts, positioned to take
OL,19,Fimages of movement within the deep
OL,20,Ffissure, where the puffins nest about
OL,21,Ftwo metres back from the entrance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
